Mmm, mumble mumble... about the boss being too rough with
his people...

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[8]Even with such a nice room provided, work seems to be tough,
huh...

I wonder if they're trying to distract from the poor working
conditions with good welfare benefits...
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[2]Could it be... that this person has the key...

Yes, yes... right there... rub there more... mmm~ yeah,
that's good...

Hehehe... That's good... right there... You're quite
skilled, aren't you...

It seems like a break room for the guards... This
organization... maybe they treat their people pretty well...
That's a pretty straightforward expression of desire.
That's a pretty straightforward expression of desire.

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[0]If we had such a big display, games and videos would be so
comfortable to watch!
For me, I'd also want a sub-display.

It's not good to place the computer directly on the floor
because it can easily get dusty, so I'd like you to
rearrange it as soon as possible!

You can have some sweets when we get back, so hold on for
now, okay?

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[2]The menu has... coffee, tea, cola, ginger ale, orange juice,
plum kelp tea, yuzu tea, Calpis, Calpis soda, oolong tea,
mountain grape soda, draft beer, sake, shochu, highball,
various cocktails...

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[2]...Jump, Magazine, Sunday...Nakayoshi, Margaret, Flowers and
Dreams, Ace, Dengeki King, Action, Zenon, Flower Party...
They've got shonen, shojo, and seinen all covered...

Even for an internet cafe, isn't this lineup a bit too
extensive...?

Yume, Ace to Dengeki King, Action to Zenon, Flower Party...
They've got shonen, shojo, and seinen all covered...

Even for a net cafe, isn't this lineup a bit too

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[2]...Jump, Magan, Sadee... Nakayoshi, Margaret, Hana to Yume,
Ace, Dengeki King, Zenon, Flower Paper... They've got
shonen, shojo, and seinen all covered...

Even for a net cafe, isn't that too much of a complete

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[2]Oh, there's a Blu-ray... let's see... "Demon-stuffed
Pussy"... "Your Rope"... "Raw Live"...
I wonder what you're looking at in the green room...
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[1]It's a really nice chair, isn't it.

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]It looks like a bunch of people in yukatas at an inn taking
a group photo... Could this possibly be...
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[8]So even evil organizations go on company trips...
It seems there are no traps in this area.
